column1: Thank you to the wonderful people of Northeast Florida for entrusting me to serve you for another term in Congress. Together we will continue to RESTORE our American way of life REBUILD the greatest American economy ever and RENEW the American Dream. #Grateful
It’s #ElectionDay. Get out and VOTE! https://t.co/LQpmEJjsh0
We can crush the virus without crushing our economy. I’m committed to keeping Northeast Florida businesses OPEN and improving on the outstanding recovery going forward. https://t.co/C9JPjtIzoV
What’s at stake?  https://t.co/3NTz94PQk3
See you soon @realDonaldTrump. Northeast Florida has your back! https://t.co/hs5pRArqBr

Thank you to the good folks of Florida’s 4th Congressional District for entrusting me with your votes today. It is a blessing to serve you in Congress and I look forward to earning your votes again on November 3rd. God Bless Northeast Florida and God Bless the USA!
The polls are open! It would be an honor to have your vote to continue fighting for Northeast Florida in Congress. Find your voting location here: https://t.co/qVFuiVAcff
Remember TOMORROW is the Republican Primary Election! Find your voting location here: https://t.co/qVFuiVAcff
For more information on early voting and where to vote on Election Day please find your county at the link below.  https://t.co/qVFuiVAcff
We are now ONE WEEK from our primary! Remember to head to the polls on Tuesday August 18. It will be an honor to have your vote and continue serving the good people of Northeast Florida. 🇺🇸

Enjoyed spending time with @NassauGOP for their Candidate Forum. Great to see so many friends like @CordByrd Club President Jonathan Petree and the other Republican candidates on the primary ballot. Don’t forget to vote August 18th! https://t.co/6XZf7S8mCQ

Had a great meeting with some of our Rutherford for Congress team of volunteers. These young men are doing a great job hitting the neighborhoods waving signs and getting out the message. Thank you guys! https://t.co/vMBTuw52wG

President Trump has always put the safety and well-being of Americans first. This was his call to make - and he made the right one. Northeast Florida may not have the RNC but we look forward to sending @realDonaldTrump back to Washington for 4 more years!
I hope you and yours are having a safe and happy 4th of July. Let’s enjoy our freedoms as Americans and vow to never let the Marxists take any of them away! #USA #ProudToBeAnAmerican
Please join me in wishing President @realDonaldTrump a Happy Birthday! https://t.co/T2nO6vlrRj
Can’t wait to welcome @realDonaldTrump to beautiful Northeast Florida on his way to four more years in the White House! #KAG #MAGA https://t.co/reClvBXCnp
Happy Birthday @VP Pence! Thank you for your leadership and love for America 🇺🇸 https://t.co/PbtxWmvAlv

This disgusting tweet is just the latest from @DonnaDeegan’s spokesperson. This type of disdain for our men and women in uniform should never be acceptable. I’m wishing a full and speedy recovery to these Guardsmen. https://t.co/XWFQ9yeVM4
